0:03:41.940,0:03:44.440
Iwe unoziva Mweya Mutsvene unobereka Mweya wa Mwari.

0:03:44.440,0:03:45.400
Unozviziva here?

0:03:45.400,0:03:54.260
Mafuta aunogamuchira, mafuta anezodzo, aunogamuchira kubva ku Mweya wa Mwari, kubva ku Mweya Mutsvene.

0:03:54.260,0:03:56.000
Anobereka.

0:03:56.000,0:04:00.980
Saka mu pfungwa imwecheteyo, mweya wakaipa uyu une basa rawo pachawo.

0:04:00.980,0:04:06.020
Basa rake ndihwo urwere ne hosha.

0:04:06.020,0:04:11.740
Hazvibviri kuti chero mu porofita asiye mweya wakaipa asi zvino oda kuporesa vanhu.

0:04:11.740,0:04:14.380
Zvakanaka, satani agere pasi apa.

0:04:14.380,0:04:20.880
Satani pachake agere uye anozvara mweya yose iyoyo yakaipa kuti iende kunoita zvinhu zvose zvakasiyana siyana.

0:04:20.880,0:04:27.000
Iwe zvino uri kudzikinura mweya wakaipa asi satani aripo akagara pasi.

0:04:27.000,0:04:30.580
Zvinonzwisisika here?

0:04:30.580,0:04:33.260
Satani aisazobvumira.

0:04:33.260,0:04:37.260
Kunyange dai aizobvumira, iye aizokuparadza.

0:04:37.260,0:04:40.120
Oo, munin'ina wangu. Iwe uri shamwari yangu - mukomana akanaka chaizvo.

0:04:40.120,0:04:41.880
Ndatenda. Ndichakuona, nhaika?

0:04:41.880,0:04:43.860
Iwe unobva kupi? - South Afrika.

0:04:43.860,0:04:45.640
Zvakanaka, South Africa. Ndatenda.

0:04:45.640,0:04:47.640
Kusunungurwa muzita ra Jesu

0:04:47.640,0:05:22.320
Nguva ye Huchapupu

0:05:22.320,0:05:26.300
Zita rangu ndi Eugene Monama. Ini ndinobva ku South Africa.

0:05:26.300,0:05:34.520
Munguva ye svondo vhiki yapera, apo munhu wa Mwari aive achinamatira munhu wese muchechi,

