0:05:41.800,0:05:49.560
uye kuti ndakabatwa chibharo, zviri zvechokwadi.

0:05:49.560,0:05:54.320
Zvose zvakatanga pazera duku.

0:05:54.320,0:05:57.460
Ndaive nemakore matanhatu panguva yazvakatanga.

0:05:57.460,0:06:03.800
Asi ini handina kunyatso ita hanya nokuti ndaive muduku zvikuru panguva iyoyo.

0:06:03.800,0:06:08.900
Kusvikira pa ndaive nemakore gumi nemashanu; ndipo pandakave ne foni yangu itsva.

0:06:08.900,0:06:16.240
Ipapo ndakatanga kutarisa tarisa pa indaneti ndikasangana ne zvinonyadzisira.

0:06:16.240,0:06:23.200
Asi zvino chinhu chisinganzwisisike chacho chaiva chekuti ndakanga ndichiona zvinonyadzisira pakati pe murume ne murume

0:06:23.200,0:06:28.420
Saka zvakaenderera mberi zvakadaro kusvikira ndava nemakore 18,

0:06:28.420,0:06:32.000
Ndakanga ndichiita gore rangu rokutanga panguva iyoyo.

0:06:32.000,0:06:39.140
Ndakanga ndichigara pa dzimba dzepachikoro panguva iyoyo saka ndaifanira kubvapo.

0:06:39.140,0:06:41.940
Ndakanyepa kuna mai wangu.

0:06:41.940,0:06:44.940
Ndakavaudza kuti ndakanga ndichigara pa chikoro

0:06:44.940,0:06:48.580
