0:06:48.580,0:06:52.200
Ndairenda imba kunze kwe pachikoro.

0:06:52.200,0:07:00.680
Pandakanga ndava nemakore gumi nemasere, ndipo pandakavhura peji yangu ye Facebook.

0:07:00.680,0:07:04.920
Uye zvakare ini ndakavhurawo zvimwewo -

0:07:04.920,0:07:12.300
iyo nzvimbo yezve kufambidzana, apo unogona kutaurirana ne varume vakasiyana siyana

0:07:12.300,0:07:18.240
Saka ndakataudzana navo, uye ipapo taizoita hurongwa.

0:07:18.240,0:07:20.660
Ndaizoonana navo, ndichivata navo.

0:07:20.660,0:07:24.240
Ndini ndaitanga kutaudzana kwacho.

0:07:24.240,0:07:27.760
Ndaingotarisa pama peji avo eFacebook

0:07:27.760,0:07:31.080
uye nekutanga hurukuro kubva ipapo.

0:07:31.080,0:07:37.480
Mhando yezvokupfeka zvandaipfeka - nokuti pandakanga ndichigara pachikoro, ndaive munhu akasiyana.

0:07:37.480,0:07:40.040
Pandakanga ndiri pa chikoro, ndaipfeka nguo dzakasiyana.

0:07:40.040,0:07:42.340
Handaizopfeka nguo idzi.

0:07:42.340,0:07:45.220
Ndaiwanzopfeka rudzi urwu rembatya pandakanga ndiri pamba.

0:07:45.220,0:07:53.340
Pese pandaienda kuchitoro chinotengesa nhumbi, ndaienda kune dhipatimendi revakadzi ndotenga zvipfeko zvevakadzi.

0:07:53.340,0:07:58.200
Zvadaro ndaizoenda kune dhipatimendi re varume kunotenga mbatya

0:07:58.200,0:08:03.640
kuitira kuti pandaienda kumba, ndaizokwanisa kupfeka zvipfeko izvozvo.

0:08:03.640,0:08:06.660
Ndakanga ndichitungamirirwa nemweya iwoyo.

0:08:06.660,0:08:10.620
Saka vabereki vako vakaona zvaiitika here?

