0:08:38.360,0:08:47.440
Uchapupu Hwe Uporofita ne Dzikinuro ya Eugene Monama

0:08:47.440,0:08:51.040
Ndiye hanzvadzi achiratidza muchidimbu

0:08:51.040,0:08:58.840
kuti aimbofamba sei ne kuyenda nenzira yechikadzi iyo yainyatsokwezva vamwe varume kwaari.

0:08:58.840,0:09:02.280
Munhu wa Mwari akataura panguva yehuprofita hwake Svondo yapera

0:09:02.280,0:09:05.560
apo hanzvadzi yakanga iri kununurwa kuti akanga ane mweya we mukadzi

0:09:05.560,0:09:08.700
uye nekuda kwaizvozvo paaiseka, aiseka semukadzi,

0:09:08.700,0:09:10.900
paaifamba, aifamba semukadzi,

0:09:10.900,0:09:13.900
uye ndizvo zvaabva kuratidza.

