Zvakanaka, muna 2015, apo ndaive ndichidzoka kubva kukirabhu, ndaive dhakadhakwa pa nguva iyoyo,

0:09:24.340,0:09:32.660
Ndakasangana ne mukomana ndichidzokera kumba.

0:09:32.660,0:09:37.160
Akakumbira kana ndaigona kuenda naye kumba kwake.

