Uye akandifefetedza kune chikwata chevarume; ndipo ndakabatwa chibharo ne chikwata chacho.

0:09:46.980,0:09:50.260
Saka kubvira ipapo, chii change chichiitika muupenyu hwako

0:09:50.260,0:09:54.080
