Vhiki yapfuura musi we Svondo taona kuti waive ugere pakati pegungano,

0:11:19.500,0:11:22.880
uye munhu wa Mwari mu Porofita T.B. Joshua akauya ndokuisa maoko pamusoro pako.

0:11:22.880,0:11:30.940
Iwe ungagone kugoverana nesu, kuti chii chawakanzwa musi we Svondo iyoyo?

0:11:30.940,0:11:36.300
Ndakanzwa sokuti mweya iwoyo wakandisiya.

