Uye takaona kuti mushure mekusunungurwa ikoko, munhu wa Mwari akarayira kuti vhudzi rako rinofanira kududunurwa.

0:11:42.540,0:11:48.940
Chii chawainzwa, zvawainzwa apo vhudzi rako raidudunurwa?

0:11:48.940,0:11:57.300
Ndakanzwa kurerukirwa, ndichiziva kuti ndasunungurwa kubva pamweya iwowo.

0:11:57.300,0:12:01.560
Iyi ndiyo hanzvadzi yatiri kuona pasikirini ye terevhizheni.

0:12:01.560,0:12:07.860
Tinoziva kuti kana Jesu Kristu atidzikinura, Anotidzikinura zvachose uye chaizvozvo.

0:12:07.860,0:12:13.260
Hupenyu hwese hwairarama munguva yekare nekuda kwe mweya we mukadzi iwowo

0:12:13.260,0:12:20.180
