0:12:32.520,0:12:34.200
Kune kubwinya kwa Mwari.

0:12:34.200,0:12:35.900
Saka enda mberi neuchapupu hwako.

0:12:35.900,0:12:42.740
Pakarepo mushure mekudzikinurwa kwangu, akakumbira kuti vhudzi rangu ribviswe.

0:12:42.740,0:12:45.200
Hongu, sezvamuri kuona.

