Mazano angu kuna avo, avo vane mweya mumwechete se wandanga ndinawo, ndee

0:13:31.380,0:13:37.460
kuti mubhuku ra VaRoma 2, Bhaibheri rinoti,

0:13:37.460,0:13:43.280
Usakopera tsika, zvipfeko kana hunhu hwenyika ino.

